metadata.name: Stableman
metadata.description:
Stablemans; They are responsible for feeding, cleaning and daily health checks of horses. All care of the horse is their responsibility for a fee. Stableman usually lives very close to the horses while doing this job. Kadir has a special room above his barn. Kadir, who establishes a strong bond with his horse, always spends time with his horse.

The photo was taken in Sanliurfa, Turkey
